                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-1204" type="surname" value="MARTIN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-1204" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN MARTIN.</persName>
                  </hi> I am a cheesemonger, at St. Marylebone—the prisoner was my errand-boy—it was his duty to receive money, and account to me for it—he was with me nearly twelve months—he left about the 8th or 10th of July—he had been with me twelve months before, and I hired him on this occasion in the absence of a boy who had a holiday—he never accounted to me for any money received of Eleanor Ann Cridge, on my account, from Colonel West.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I know I paid my master.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
