               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184708160216"></xptr>
               <p>Mr. Martin supplies us with butter and eggs—On the 3rd of August the prisoner came with some butter and eggs—he brought this bill, for 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>), I saw him write a receipt to it—I paid him a sovereign, a half-crown, two sixpences, and twopence.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
