                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-1206" type="given" value="PAUL"></interp>PAUL JONES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) On Saturday night, about half-past nine o'clock, I met Mr. Martin with the prisoner—he gave him in charge—I told the prisoner what he was charged with—he said he knew nothing about it, and directly afterwards said, "Master had me up for this once before."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I paid my master on the Saturday night; he was by the butter-place at the time; he put the money into his pocket.</p>
